    "\n",
    "**Inputs**: `vagus_atlas_dataset.xlsx` · `vagus_segment_scaffold.xlsx`\n",
    "**Outputs**:\n",
    "- `vagus_atlas_full.xlsx`\n",
    "- `vagus_atlas_analysis.xlsx`\n",
    "- `overview_table_registered_v2_tiefix.csv` *(used as Table 1)*\n",
    "\n",
    "**Runtime**: ~10–20 s\n"
   ]
